reviewText: A pretty good play.  Leon played a different role than what I am used to him playing, but all in all it was a good play.
Title: From This Day Forward

reviewText: This uplifting TV movie is a great movie about love, trust and marriage.  The actors Leon from the Temptations, Essence Atkins from Half and Half, Vanessa Simmons from Run's house, JoMarie Payton from Family Matters, Marcus T. gray and Antwan Tanner makes a great cast.  My daughter and I love this and all other GMC/UP TV movies/plays.
Title: From This Day Forward
